---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative bg-zt-dark text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/3 w-[40%] h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zt-primary/30 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-5 fade-up">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <img src="/zt.png" alt="A&A ZentrIT" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" />
          <div class="flex flex-col leading-tight">
            <span class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-sans font-semibold text-white/80">
              Zentr<span class="text-zt-primary font-bold">IT</span>
            </span>
            <span class="text-[0.5rem] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-mono text-white/30">arquitectura digital</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed max-w-xs font-light">
          Diseño de precisión. Ingeniería implacable. Construimos infraestructura digital para empresas que no aceptan concesiones.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3 fade-up">
        <h4 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-semibold text-zt-primary mb-5 font-mono">Navegación</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="#nucleo" class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300 font-light">El Núcleo</a></li>
          <li><a href="#servicios" class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300 font-light">Capacidades</a></li>
          <li><a href="#proyectos" class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300 font-light">Sistemas</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contacto" class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300 font-light">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4 fade-up">
        <h4 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-semibold text-zt-primary mb-5 font-mono">Contacto</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light">
            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:zentritsoft@gmail.com" class="hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300">zentritsoft@gmail.com</a>
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light">
            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Teléfonos</span>
            <span>933 070 052 / 912 077 181</span>
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light">
            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Ubicación</span>
            <span>Chimbote, Perú</span>
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light">
            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Instagram</span>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/zentritsoft" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300">@zentritsoft</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs text-white/30 font-light">
      <span>&copy; {currentYear} A&amp;A ZentrIT. Todos los derechos reservados.</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300">Aviso de Privacidad</a>
        <span class="w-px h-3 bg-white/10"></span>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-zt-primary transition-all duration-300">Términos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
